speech: The router may be using a default wireless frequency channel. The default channels are 1,6, and 11. Try selecting a  less crowded channel. You can manually change channels by logging in to your router admin. Did this solve the issue?

Older models do not look for a less crowded channel. The router may be using the default channel which is 1,6, or 11. If this is the case please try switching to a less crowded frequency channel. Login into the router admin and manually change the channel there. Does this solve the issue?
